  "emotion": "frustration",
  "valence": "negative",
  "arousal": "high",
  "confidence": 0.95,
  "reasoning": "The user is asking for a reason ('why') which makes this a question. The mention of multiple restarts and 'keep crashing' indicates frustration. The exclamation marks suggest high arousal."
